{"tid":1918290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平已到達武漢 視察疫情防控工作","createTime":"2020-03-10T03:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T04:38:44.000Z","uid":89543,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4c71ab654004ee6962a088bc3badbfe739cc6ce6","tid":1918290,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200310/_2020031011311057745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200310%2F_2020031011311057745.jpg&h=83705772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地新冠肺炎疫情緩和，國家主席習近平10日早上乘飛機抵達湖北省武漢市，考察湖北和武漢新冠肺炎疫情防控工作，並看望慰問奮戰在一線的廣大醫務工作者、解放軍指戰員、社區工作者、公安幹警、基層幹部、下沈幹部、志願者和患者群眾、社區居民。"},{"pid":"651e405e3e011c0bec0945ab5adfa6522ea7b125","tid":1918290,"uid":89543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:59:01.000Z","msg":"習大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb795cc1ff0e8e5d827ff3b21e61859cb9cdd1fb","tid":1918290,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:59:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1219156/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%8A%B5%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2-%E8%A6%96%E5%AF%9F%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1219156%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2-%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSn4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=2451dfae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1219156%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%